  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But in-- in-- in the-- in the conflict, in the dialect, you have-- you developed the survival of the Jewry because from this moment, we have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But haved later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is the 18th century. 19th century, we have the [? scholar. ?] We have-- we have [? medicine. ?] We have what-- what probably gives the Jews the Jewish Yiddish language.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And by the 20th century, but Vilna, we have-- we have usually the labor-- development of labor, developed the Hebrew-- Hebrew language, and the Zionism.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Vilna was at center.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Vilna had the seminars.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Vilna had-- Vilna had the-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Vilna collected-- collected practically the all was the Yerushalayim, the leader.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Jew-- the-- its youth was politically oriented.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews were continuously almost-- almost an inspiration.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have drugs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have the-- the-- the-- the idea of us was-- was continuously discussions of the-- about the life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Imagine, this little Vilna had four-- four Hebrew gymnasium-- Gymnasium [NON-ENGLISH], Tarbut, and one Yiddish gymnasium, Real Gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In addition, it's had 12 gymnasiums with the high schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In addition, a seminar what was rabbinical seminar, what was send out the rabbis all over the-- all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In addition, they had technical schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had-- they had-- a cultural life what-- what practically the [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jewry ?] would serve as inspiration for-- for-- for-- for the entire Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- in the beginning, in the primary school, I went to the Hebrew school and was [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Chojnow. ?] After that, in 1935, I was transferred to a public school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After I graduated from-- from public school, I went to Gymnasium Epstein.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I want to give you a few stories, a few memories from my-- from my schooling.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
